        <p>This position will report to the three Cardinal Rose Group partners and will be responsible for performing all accounting functions and financial reporting activities including, but not limited to full cycle G/L, A/R, A/P, T&E, F/A, I/C, cash, the month-end close process and will be responsible for financial statement preparation, management reporting, budgeting and forecasting, treasury management, financial statement audits, income & VAT taxes, and general administration.  In addition, this person will be responsible for designing, developing, and maintaining policies and procedures that are GAAP compliant and supportive of the business. </p>
